<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id6c0f83e2-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDateOfAmendment" id="id6c0f83e3-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date of 1978 Amendment</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">For effective date of amendment by <ref href="/us/pl/95/302">Pub. L. 95–302</ref>, see <ref href="/us/pl/95/302/s2">section 2 of Pub. L. 95–302</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t33/s1487">section 1487 of this title</ref>.</p>
